 the second set, scintillating shot-making alongside rousing defence with Alcaraz fighting off the final's 14th break point in the third game.\", \"from\": 1877, \"to\": 2041, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1973, \"end\": 1980, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 0.9999999999554348, \"rank\": 3.0059771806688435e-11, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no let-up\", \"from\": 1887, \"to\": 1896}, {\"ngram\": \"the second set\", \"from\": 1900, \"to\": 1914}, {\"ngram\": \"shot-making\", \"from\": 1930, \"to\": 1941}, {\"ngram\": \"defence\", \"from\": 1960, \"to\": 1967}, {\"ngram\": \"the final's 14th break point\", \"from\": 1994, \"to\": 2022}, {\"ngram\": \"the third game\", \"from\": 2026, \"to\": 2040}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Again the set was decided by a tie-break and it was Djokovic with history on the line again sweeping through to take victory after two hours and 50 minutes.\", \"from\": 2043, \"to\": 2199, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2095, \"end\": 2103, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6646463230300516e-19, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the set\", \"from\": 2049, \"to\": 2056}, {\"ngram\": \"a tie-break\", \"from\": 2072, \"to\": 2083}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 2109, \"to\": 2116}, {\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 2120, \"to\": 2128}, {\"ngram\": \"victory\", \"from\": 2160, \"to\": 2167}, {\"ngram\": \"two hours\", \"from\": 2174, \"to\": 2183}, {\"ngram\": \"50 minutes\", \"from\": 2188, \"to\": 2198}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lorenzo Musetti defeated Felix Auger-Aliassime in three sets on Saturday to claim the bronze medal, giving Italy its first men's tennis medal in 100 years.\", \"from\": 2201, \"to\": 2356, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2201, \"end\": 2216, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lorenzo_Musetti\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lorenzo Musetti\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lorenzo_Musetti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lorenzo_Musetti\"}, {\"begin\": 2226, \"end\": 2247, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/F\\u00e9lix_Auger-Aliassime\", \"score\": 0.9999999516558103, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Felix Auger-Aliassime\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/F\\u00e9lix_Auger-Aliassime\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/F\\u00e9lix_Auger-Aliassime\"}, {\"begin\": 2308, \"end\": 2313, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9997460621277242, \"rank\": 0.00022966539685934857, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"three sets\", \"from\": 2251, \"to\": 2261}, {\"ngram\": \"Saturday\", \"from\": 2265, \"to\": 2273}, {\"ngram\": \"the bronze medal\", \"from\": 2283, \"to\": 2299}, {\"ngram\": \"its first men's tennis medal\", \"from\": 2314, \"to\": 2342}, {\"ngram\": \"100 years\", \"from\": 2346, \"to\": 2355}]}, {\"sentence\": \"HOUSE RULES\", \"from\": 2360, \"to\": 2371, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"HOUSE RULES\", \"from\": 2360, \"to\": 2371}]}]}"